data.description: Welcome! Incredibly well-loved/maintained home on perfectly level-lot! Home is much larger than it looks. Greeted rocking-chair porch & soaring ceilings inside, bedroom on main w/ full bath. Kitchen w/ granite countertops & ample counterspace extension. Impressive dining room w/ incredible natural light- the large/bay area is the flex rm you've been needing! Dining area leads to deck & fenced-in pool. Pool w/ new pool pump ('20), new liner ('23) & gazebo for the right amount of shade. Sprawling/level backyard. Upstairs boasts 2 bedroom suites (can strategically be separate bedrms) & full bathrm. Bedrm on left features balcony to enjoy the serene & private backyard. Outdoor shed & much more! Great location with proximity to Downtown and Peek Forest Park.
